    Main module:
    
        stderr, stdin, stdout -> Standard file descriptors
        init()   -> Initialize any PrimaLuce program. 

    FileSystem module:                

        open()   -> Open file
        close()  -> Close file
        flush()  -> Flush data to file        
        lines()  -> Opens the given file and returns an iterator function that
                    each time it's called returns a new line from file.
        read()   -> Reads form file
        write()  -> Writes to file descriptor
        seek()   -> Seek's through file      

        chown()  -> Owner
        chmod()  -> Permissions

        fstat()  -> File info Structure

    Process module:
    
        fork()   -> Fork a process
        exec()   -> Exec a process
        kill()   -> Send kill signal to a process
        pid()    -> Get process id
        umask()  -> File creation mode

        setuid() -> User id
        getuid() 
        setgid() -> Group id
        getgid()        

